e%20Officials%20%26quot%3BAccidentally%26quot%3B%20Shared%20Yemen%20War%20Plan%20With%20Journalist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20journalist%20was%20inadvertently%20included%20in%20a%20group%20chat%20in%20which%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%2C%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20and%20other%20top%20American%20officials%20discussed%20upcoming%20strikes%20against%20Yemen's%20Huthi%20rebels%2C%20the%20White%20House%20confirmed%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20the%20strikes%20on%20March%2015%2C%20but%20in%20a%20shocking%20security%20breach%2C%20The%20Atlantic%20magazine's%20editor-in-chief%20Jeffrey%20Goldberg%20wrote%20that%20he%20had%20hours%20of%20advance%20notice%20via%20the%20group%20chat%20on%20Signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20message%20thread%20that%20was%20reported%20appears%20to%20be%20authentic%2C%20and%20we%20are%20reviewing%20how%20an%20inadvertent%20number%20was%20added%20to%20the%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20Brian%20Hughes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20said%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20have%20the%20utmost%20confidence%20in%20his%20national%20security%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20US%20president%20earlier%20said%20he%20did%20not%20%26quot%3Bknow%20anything%20about%26quot%3B%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leak%20could%20have%20been%20highly%20damaging%20if%20Goldberg%20had%20publicized%20details%20of%20the%20plan%20in%20advance%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20do%20so%20even%20after%20the%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%2C%20however%2C%20write%20that%20Hegseth%20sent%20information%20on%20the%20strikes%2C%20including%20on%20%26quot%3Btargets%2C%20weapons%20the%20US%20would%20be%20deploying%2C%20and%20attack%20sequencing%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20lengthy%20Hegseth%20text%2C%20the%20first%20detonations%20in%20Yemen%20would%20be%20felt%20two%20hours%20hence%2C%20at%201%3A45%20pm%20eastern%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldberg%20wrote%20--%20a%20timeline%20that%20was%20borne%20out%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoldberg%20said%20he%20was%20added%20to%20the%20group%20chat%20two%20days%20earlier%2C%20and%20received%20messages%20from%20other%20top%20government%20officials%20designating%20representatives%20who%20would%20work%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2014%2C%20a%20person%20identified%20as%20Vance%20expressed%20doubts%20about%20carrying%20out%20the%20strikes%2C%20saying%20he%20hated%20%26quot%3Bbailing%20Europe%20out%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20countries%20there%20were%20more%20affected%20by%20Huthi%20attacks%20on%20shipping%20than%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Stunning%20and%20dangerous'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20chat%20contributors%20identified%20as%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Hegseth%20both%20sent%20messages%20arguing%20only%20Washington%20had%20the%20capability%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20strikes%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20official%20saying%20he%20shared%20Vance's%20%26quot%3Bloathing%20of%20European%20free-loading.%20It's%20PATHETIC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20person%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3BS%20M%26quot%3B%20--%20possibly%20Trump%20advisor%20Stephen%20Miller%20--%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20US%20successfully%20restores%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20at%20great%20cost%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20some%20further%20economic%20gain%20extracted%20in%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20breach%20provoked%20outrage%20among%20Democrats%2C%20with%20Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20stunning%20breaches%20of%20military%20intelligence%20I%20have%20read%20about%20in%20a%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time%26quot%3B%20and%20calling%20for%20a%20full%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Jack%20Reed%20also%20slammed%20the%20leak%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20carelessness%20shown%20by%20President%20Trump's%20cabinet%20is%20stunning%20and%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Hillary%20Clinton%20--%20who%20was%20repeatedly%20attacked%20by%20Trump%20for%20using%20a%20private%20email%20server%20while%20she%20was%20secretary%20of%20state%20--%20posted%20the%20Atlantic%20article%20on%20X%20along%20with%20the%20message%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20got%20to%20be%20kidding%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Huthi%20attacks%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Huthi%20rebels%2C%20who%20have%20controlled%20much%20of%20Yemen%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Baxis%20of%20resistance%26quot%3B%20of%20pro-Iran%20groups%20staunchly%20opposed%20to%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20launched%20scores%20of%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks%20at%20ships%20passing%20Yemen%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20during%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Huthis'%20campaign%20crippled%20the%20vital%20route%2C%20which%20normally%20carries%20about%2012%20percent%20of%20world%20shipping%20traffic%2C%20forcing%20many%20companies%20into%20a%20costly%20detour%20around%20the%20tip%20of%20southern%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20began%20targeting%20the%20Huthis%20in%20response%20under%20the%20previous%20administration%20of%20president%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20and%20has%20launched%20repeated%20rounds%20of%20strikes%20on%20Huthi%20targets%2C%20some%20with%20British%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%20overwhelming%20lethal%20force%20until%20we%20have%20achieved%20our%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20the%20Huthis'%20threats%20against%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%2C%20and%20US%20strikes%20have%20continued%20over%20the%20past%2010%20days.%3