ng%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20stomach%20dropped%20and%20I%20immediately%20felt%20tears%20sting%20my%20eyes.%20I%20pushed%20them%20back%2C%20finished%20paying%2C%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20ballet%20class%2C%20five%20minutes%20away.%20Parent%20viewing%20is%20an%20annual%20event%2C%20a%20milestone%20following%20months%20of%20practice%20and%20one%20I'd%20looked%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20studio%2C%20my%20daughter%20locked%20eyes%20with%20me.%20I%20could%20tell%20from%20her%20trembling%20lips%20that%20she'd%20been%20putting%20on%20a%20brave%20face%20in%20class%2C%20but%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-parents-make-that-can-hurt-kids-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20was%20hurt%20and%20confused%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20my%20absence%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20a%20post-class%20meltdown.%20I%20felt%20like%20the%20worst%20parent%20in%20the%20world.%20Every%20other%20week%2C%20I'd%20spent%20class%20time%20in%20the%20waiting%20room.%20Why%20did%20I%20have%20to%20run%20errands%20that%20day%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288f8537c-8af8-4f8c-8ee2-991c43ad92e8%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20see%20myself%20as%20anything%20other%20than%20a%20forgetful%20mother%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20class%2C%20my%20daughter%20held%20her%20tears%20until%20she%20was%20in%20her%20car%20seat.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20were%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20wept.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20the%20other%20parents%20were%20there%20smiling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-facing-my-sons-bullies-helped-heal-wounds-my-past-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewords%20made%20me%20cry%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20too.%20I%20got%20out%20of%20the%20driver's%20seat%20and%20went%20over%20to%20embrace