0at%20a%20tenuous%20moment%20for%20TikTok.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20company%20is%20currently%20reckoning%20with%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-details-when-how-legal-cases-trump-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edivest-or-ban%20law%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20requires%20its%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20to%20separate%20itself%20from%20its%20US%20app.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20app%20is%20operating%20in%20the%20US%20based%20on%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20gave%20TikTok%20until%20April%205%20to%20sort%20out%20a%20political%20resolution%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20move%20follows%20other%20recent%20departures%20from%20executives%2C%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-top-music-exec-ole-obermann-is-leaving-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOle%20Obermann%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20global%20head%20of%20music%20business%20development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20Chandlee's%20full%20memo%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHey%20all%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20Shou%20has%20just%20shared%2C%20as%20we%20strive%20towards%202025%20goals%20and%20beyond%2C%20we%20have%20had%20many%20discussions%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20business%20and%20how%20to%20continue%20transforming%20our%20model.%20Notably%2C%20how%20we%20continue%20to%20move%20faster%20together%20in%20continued%20development%20of%20automated%20capabilities%20and%20deep%20integration%20into%20planning%20systems%2C%20TikTok%20Shop%2C%20and%20measurement%20%26amp%3B%20ecosystem%20partners.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20our%20offerings%20become%20more%20technical%20and%20our%20client%20product%20solutions%20become%20more%20sophisticated%20to%20provide%20even%20more%20value%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20Global%20Business%20Solutions%20(GBS)%20and%20Global%20Monetization%20Product%20Technology%20(GMPT)%20operate%20increasingly%20hand-in-hand.%20To%20enable%20this%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20it's%20best%20to%20streamline%20under%20one%20department%20lead%20and%20will%20be%20scaling%20back%20my%20day-to-day%20role%20to%20an%20advisory%20one.%20Leaders%20of%20both%20organizations%20will%20report%20directly%20to%20Will%20Liu%2C%20effective%20April%201.%20I%20want%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20share%20my%20perspective%20with%20you%20on%20why%20I%20believe%20it%20is%20the%20right%20decision%20moving%20forward.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20we%20have%20built%20something%20that%20has%20never%20been%20built%20before.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20joined%20a%20start-up%20whose%20user%20base%20was%20growing%20fast%20based%20on%20a%20simple%20concept%20of%20short%20form%20video%20combined%20with%20music%2C%20creating%20a%20unique%20entertainment%20experience.%20A%20small%20group%20of%20us%2C%20split%20between%20shared%20working%20spaces%20in%20NY%2C%20London%2C%20and%20LA%20were%20tasked%20with%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20engage%20with%20this%20audience%20and%20introducing%20ads%20into%20the%20mix%20to%20create%20the%20first%20ads%20business%20on%20TikTok.%20We%20didn't%20have%20a%20name%2C%20but%20came%20up%20with%20Global%20Business%20Solutions%20as%20it%20sounded%20impressive%2C%20and%20thus%20formed%20GBS.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThat%20humble%20beginning%20has%20turned%20into%20the%20fastest%20growing%20ads%20business%20in%20the%20world%20(outside%20of%20Douyin)%2C%20achieving%20our%20current%20revenue%20levels%20two%20years%20ahead%20of%20Meta%20and%20four%20years%20ahead%20of%20Google.%20And%20we%20are%20not%20done%20yet%2C%20as%20we%20ambitiously%20target%2050%25%20growth%20again%20in%202025.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20has%20not%20been%20a%20linear%20process.%20We%20have%20encountered%20a%20ban%20in%20India%2C%20a%20global%20pandemic%20where%20we%20all%20worked%20from%20home%20for%20two%20years%2C%20geo-political%20headwinds%2C%20wars%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Middle%20East%2C%20increased%20regulatory%20oversight%2C%20and%20more.%20All%20that%20said%2C%20the%20things%20we%20have%20always%20focused%20on%20are%20our%20clients%20and%20how%20we%20can%20best%20deliver%20business%20outcomes%20for%20them%20based%20on%20the%20tools%20and%20products%20we%20had%20at%20each%20point%20in%20the%20journey.%20Remember%2C%20as%20we%20were%20building%20GBS%2C%20the%20product%20and%20engineering%20teams%20were%20rapidly%20building%20capabilities%20for%20our%20clients%20to%20identify%2C%20reach%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20measure%20our%20global%20audiences.%20This%20focus%20on%20building%20relevant%20and%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20clients%20has%20fueled%20our%20teams%20around%20the%20world%2C%20large%20and%20small.%20Along%20with%20the%20trust%20each%20of%20YOU%20have%20built%20with%20your%20clients%2C%20agencies%2C%20and%20partners%2C%20this%20combo%20has%20been%20the%20foundation%20of%20this%20growth%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20be.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWill%20and%20I%20were%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20thinking%20how%20we%20can%20communicate%20better%2C%20deliver%20client%20feedback%20faster%2C%20launch%20products%20more%20smoothly%2C%20be%20more%20transparent%20and%20accountable%2C%20and%20ultimately%20learn%20and%20iterate%20to%20get%20to%20market%20faster.%20What%20became%20more%20obvious%20was%20that%20our%20structure%20was%20slowing%20us%20down.%20I%20have%20always%20encouraged%20our%20teams%20to%20think%20differently%2C%20be%20transformative%2C%20and%20not%20let%20the%20past%20limit%20the%20future.%20By%20aligning%20the%20GBS%20org%20directly%20with%20the%20product%20org%2C%20we%20can%20truly%20move%20as%20one%20team.%20Will%20is%20an%20exceptional%20product%20and%20eng%20leader%20who%20has%20built%20strong%20teams%20and%20products%20globally.%20He%20is%20respected%20by%20the%20sales%20leaders%20and%20has%20a%20true%20focus%20on%20delivering%20best%20in%20class%20solutions%20for%20our%20clients.%20This%20change%20is%20an%20example%20of%20Will%20and%20I%20eating%20our%20own%20dogfood.%20We%20are%20being%20disruptive%20to%20allow%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business.%20To%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20traditional%20way%20of%20thinking%20about%20an%20organization%20and%20may%20feel%20uncomfortable%20for%20some.%20It%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20decision%20for%20me%20especially%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20right%20one%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20If%20executed%20correctly%2C%20the%20business%2C%20and%20therefore%20clients%2C%20will%20benefit.%20For%20all%20of%20us%2C%20this%20will%20come%20down%20to%20trusting%20and%20believing%20in%20this%20decision%2C%20then%20committing%20to%20execution.%20It's%20that%20simple.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20for%20me%2C%20I've%20always%20wanted%20to%20lead%20with%20honesty%20and%20openness%20and%20want%20you%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20very%20comfortable%20with%20this.%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20have%20built%20and%20grateful%20to%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20this%20amazing%20story%20that%20will%20continue%20through%20you!%20I%20have%20said%20this%20before%2C%20I%20love%20to%20build%20and%20for%20this%20last%20chapter%2C%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20build%20a%20part%20of%20history.%20I%20am%20so%20lucky%20for%20the%20opportunity%20given%20to%20me%20by%20Lidong%20almost%20six%20years%20ago%20to%20the%20day.%20He%20trusted%20me%20and%20I%20have%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20him%20and%20Shou%20over%20the%20years%20on%20how%20to%20push%20myself%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%20and%20to%20continue%20to%20push%20my%20boundaries.%20I%20won't%20be%20going%20anywhere%20soon%2C%20you%20will%20see%20me%20around%20and%20over%20time%2C%20that%20too%20shall%20fade%20but%20I%20will%20leave%20you%20with%20this.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20are%20building%20history.%20Books