t-game-1236346656%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Spikes%20Husband's%20Food%2C%20Kills%20Him%20With%20Mother's%20Help%20In%20Bengaluru%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2037-year-old%20real-estate%20businessman%20was%20allegedly%20murdered%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20mother-in-law%20over%20his%20alleged%20multiple%20extramarital%20affairs%20and%20illegal%20business%20dealings%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20week%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20incident%20came%20to%20light%20when%20the%20body%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20Loknath%20Singh%2C%20was%20found%20by%20a%20few%20people%20in%20an%20abandoned%20car%20in%20a%20deserted%20area%20in%20Chikkabanavara%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20received%20a%20distress%20call%20on%20112%20at%205.30pm%20on%20Saturday%2C%20informing%20us%20about%20the%20body.%20We%20have%20arrested%20his%20wife%20and%20mother-in-law%20for%20the%20crime.%20Further%20investigation%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20Bangalore%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20Saidul%20Adavath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20a%20preliminary%20probe%20into%20the%20crime%20revealed%20the%20accused%20initially%20spiked%20the%20man's%20food%20with%20sleeping%20pills%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20him%20feel%20drowsy.%20They%20then%20drove%20him%20to%20a%20secluded%20spot%20where%20they%20slit%20his%20throat%20with%20a%20knife%20before%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20also%20attributed%20the%20killing%20to%20the%20victim's%20alleged%20extramarital%20affairs%20and%20illegal%20business%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20that%20Loknath%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20woman%20for%20two%20years%20before%20the%20couple%20registered%20their%20marriage%20in%20Kunigal%20in%20Decemb