%20Green%20Card%2C%20H-1B%20Visa%2C%20F-1%20Visa%20Holders%20Cautioned%20Over%20Travelling%20Abroad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20recently%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BA%20green%20card%20does%20not%20give%20an%20individual%20an%20indefinite%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20United%20States%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20statement%20that%20has%20become%20a%20cause%20of%20much%20anxiety%20and%20stress%20for%20millions%20of%20immigrants%20of%20Indian%20origin.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%2C%20US%20immigration%20rules%20have%20been%20tightened%20significantly%2C%20prompting%20immigration%20attorneys%20to%20issue%20travel%20risk%20advisories%20for%20Indian%20Green%20Card%20and%20H-1B%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20massive%20crackdown%20on%20immigrants%20-%20both%20illegal%20and%20legal%20-%20key%20immigration%20agencies%20of%20the%20US%20have%20enhanced%20scrutiny%20of%20those%20travelling%20abroad%20and%20even%20more%20greatly%20heightened%20checks%20for%20those%20who%20return%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20agencies%20that%20keep%20a%20check%20of%20who%20is%20leaving%20or%20entering%20the%20United%20States%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20or%20USCIS%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EImmigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20or%20ICE%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDepartment%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20or%20DHS%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECustoms%20and%20Border%20Protection%20or%20CBP%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Indians%20living%2C%20working%20or%20studying%20in%20the%20US%20hold%20either%20a%20Green%20Card%20or%20an%20H-1B%20or%20F-1%20visas.%20These%20have%20now%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20at%20a%20port%20of%20entry%20while%20returning%20to%20the%20US.%20While%20permanent%20residents%20and%20legal%20visa%20holders%20don't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20status%20of%20their%20residency%20or%20work%20validity%2C%20these%20enhanced%20checks%20will%20definitely%20be%20a%20test%20of%20their%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnhanced%20checks%20have%20begun%20after%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20plans%20to%20curb%20or%20restrict%20people%20from%2043%20nations%20to%20enter%20the%20United%20States.%20In%20India's%20immediate%20neighbourhood%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Bhutan%20are%20on%20that%20list.%20Though%20Indians%2C%20who%20are%20known%20to%20be%20law-abiding%20and%20tax-paying%20individuals%2C%20are%20not%20on%20any%20travel%20ban%20or%20restricted%20list%2C%20immigration%20attorneys%20have%20advised%20greater%20caution%20while%20planning%20travel%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeightened%20checks%2C%20they%20say%2C%20have%20resulted%20in%20a%20massive%20backlog%20in%20visa%20stamping.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20getting%20detained%20have%20also%20surged%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20The%20backlog%20is%20not%20just%20at%20the%20port%20of%20entry%2C%20but%20also%20across%20US%20embassies%20and%20consulates%20globally%2C%20which%20are%20facing%20huge%20administrative%20challenges%20due%20to%20the%20updated%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplication%20and%20documentation%20scrutiny%20have%20now%20got%20to%20go%20through%20additional%20reviews%20at%20every%20stage%2C%20leading%20to%20unprecedented%20delays.%20Documentation%20is%20reportedly%20getting%20stuck%20with%20no%20clear%20reasons%20being%20given%20as%20to%20why%20it%20is%20happening.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20time%20frame%20to%20process%20an%20application%20is%20getting%20stretched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20experts%20have%20advised%20Green%20Card%20(permanent%20residents)%2C%20H-1B%20(highly-skilled%20professionals)%2C%20and%20F-1%20(students)%20visa%20holders%20to%20keep%20the%20following%20check-list%20in%20mind%20while%20making%20travel%20plans%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPassport%20of%20the%20traveller's%20home%20country%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EValid%20Green%20Card%20(Form%20I-551)%20-%20document%20must%20not%20be%20expired.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EValid%20and%20unexpired%20H-1B%20or%20F-1%20visa%2C%20permitting%20multiple%20entries%20into%20the%20US%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUS%20Re-Entry%20Permit%20(wherever%20applicable)%20-%20For%20those%20travelling%20out%20of%20the%20US%20for%20more%20than%201%20year%2C%20but%20less%20than%202%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEmployment%20verification%20letter%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EW-2%20form%20and%20proof%20of%20payment%20of%20federal%20income%20tax%20for%20the%20previous%20one%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPayslip%2C%20salary%20slip%2C%20or%20valid%20income%20proof%20for%20the%20most%20recent%203%20months%20(provided%20by%20employer)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EValid%20letter%20from%20the%20college%20or%20university%20stating%20the%20duration%20of%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EValid%20documents%20of%20US%20bank%20accounts%20(at%20least%20one%20primary%20account)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EValid%20US%20driving%20licence%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20experts%20have%20advised%20travellers%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThose%20who%20are%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20after%20an%20extended%20stay%20overseas%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20detailed%20and%20lengthy%20Q%26amp%3BA%20sessions%20with%20Customs%20and%20Border%20officials.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECooperate%20and%20remain%20calm%20throughout%20the%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecondary%20inspections%20may%20take%20over%20two%20hours%20to%20clear%20at%20a%20port%20of%20entry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20stay%20of%20more%20than%20six%20months%20outside%20the%20US%20is%20likely%20to%20result%20in%20additional%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20let%20your%20Green%20Card%20or%20visa%20expire.%20Renew%20them%20well%20before%20the%20expiry%20date.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20person's%20Green%20Card%20is%20revoked%2C%20an%20option%20is%20available%20to%20file%20for%20an%20appeal%20with%20the%20USCIS%20or%20immigration%20court.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThose%20who%20have%20finished%20their%20education%20in%20the%20US%20under%20an%20F-1%20visa%20and%20have%20switched%20to%20an%20H-1B%20or%20other%20work%20visa%2C%20may%20face%20extended%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThose%20whose%20H-1B%20visa%20expired%20more%20than%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20have%20filed%20for%20an%20extension%20or%20renewal%20may%20face%20additional%20scrutiny.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742841420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F85btsje8_h1b-visa-istock_625x300_06_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-green-card-h-1b-visa-f-1-visa-holders-cautioned-over-travelling-abroad-8002265%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Due%20to%20the%20Trump%20Administration's%20massive%20crackdown%20on%20immigrants%20-%20both%20illegal%20and%20legal%20-%20key%20immigration%20agencies%20of%20the%20US%20have%20enhanced%20scrutiny%20of%20those%20travelling%20abroad%20and%20even%20more%20greatly%20heightened%20checks%20for%20those%20returning%20to%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BYD's%20sales%20soar%20as%20Chinese%20auto%20giant%20captures%20world's%20attention%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742841263000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyd-s-sales-soar-as-chinese-auto-giant-captures-world-s-attention-125032500004_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shenzhen-based%20BYD%20reported%20revenue%20of%20777%20billion%20yuan%20(%24107%20billion)%20for%20the%2012%20months%20ended%20Dec.%2031%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%