20the%20former%20Kingdom%20of%20Sanga%20and%20Rana%20Pratap%2C%20where%20there%20is%20still%20a%20repository%20of%20collective%20memories.%C2%A0The%20matter%20had%20ripples%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20today%20and%20a%20right-wing%20Rajput%20group%2C%20Karni%20Sena%2C%20has%20threatened%20that%20they%20will%20%26quot%3Bchop%20off%20the%20tongue%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20comments%20by%20another%20leader%20of%20his%20party%2C%20Abu%20Azmi%2C%20who%20had%20praised%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb.%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20Hindu%20groups%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20what%20they%20called%20attempts%20to%20glorify%20Aurangzeb%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20unleashed%20atrocities%20on%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20SAMAJWADI%20PARTY%20MP%20SAID%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0purported%20video%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman's%20had%20surfaced%20recently%20in%20which%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20that%20Rana%20Sanga%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B%20who%20brought%20Babur%20to%20defeat%20Ibrahim%20Lodi.%C2%A0Then%2C%20during%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Suman%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20comments%20linking%20d%20Rana%20Sanga%20to%20Babur's%20invasion%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20often%20claim%20that%20Muslims%20have%20the%20DNA%20of%20Babur.%20But%20who%20invited%20Babur%20to%20India%3F%20It%20was%20Rana%20Sanga%20who%20brought%20him%20to%20defeat%20Ibrahim%20Lodi.%20By%20that%20logic%2C%20if%20Muslims%20are%20Babur's%20descendants%2C%20you%20are%20also%20the%20descendants%20of%20Rana%20Sanga%20--%20a%20traitor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20in%20India%20do%20not%20idolise%20any%20Mughal%20emperor%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20consider%20Mohammed%20Sahab%20and%20Sufi%20saints'%20traditions%20as%20their%20ideals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETROUBLE%20IN%20ASSEMBLY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20today%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Shrichand%20Kriplani%20opposed%20this%20statement%20through%20Point%20of%20Information%20and%20demanded%20parliamentary%20action.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20raised%20the%20issue%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20Harimohan%20Sharma%20objected%20and%20said%20that%20this%20topic%20cannot%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20House.%20At%20this%2C%20BJP%20MLAs%20registered%20strong%20protest%20and%20targeted%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20slogans%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20questioned%20why%20the%20insult%20of%20Rana%20Sanga%20cannot%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwaraj%20Mewar%2C%20an%20erstwhile%20royal%20from%20Mewar%2C%20has%20slammed%20SP%20leader%20over%20remarks%20on%20Rana%20Sanga.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20misleading%20the%20people%20by%20giving%20misinformation%20in%20the%20upper%20house%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20divide%20in%20the%20society%20by%20making%20such%20comments%20they%20have%20not%20only%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Rajasthanis%20but%20of%20India%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EROW%20REACHES%20DELHI%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20days%2C%20discussions%20are%20happening%20on%20historical%20figures.%20While%20someone%20crticises%20the%20great%20and%20glorious%20king%20like%20Rana%20Sanga%20saying%20he%20betrayed%20the%20country%2C%20others%20are%20busy%20advocating%20Aurangzeb%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETourism%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20has%20called%20it%20a%20distortion%20of%20history.%20%26quot%3BThe%20spirit%20of%20independence%20that%20Maharana%20Sanga%20ignited%20not%20only%20saved%20India%20from%20being%20enslaved%20but%20also%20gave%20a%20huge%20contribution%20in%20keeping%20the%20culture%20of%20India%20eternal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%20Only%20people%20with%20%26quot%3Btrivial%20intellect%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20heart%26quot%3B%20make%20such%20statements%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRana%20Sanga%20has%20been%20the%20identity%20of%20Bharat.%20Throughout%20his%20life%2C%20he%20fought%20against%20Babar%20and%20other%20invaders.%20Glorifying%20an%20invader%20instead%20of%20the%20one%20who%20protected%20the%20country%20is%20quite%20indecent%20and%20inappropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Shashank%20Mani%20termed%20the%20SP%20MP's%20remarks%20as%20%26quot%3Bcondemnable%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20the%20people%20should%20salute%20great%20men%20like%20Rana%20Sanga%20instead%20of%20making%20such%20%26quot%3Binappropriate%26quot%3B%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAKHILESH%20YADAV'S%20GALILEO%20JIBE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20attacked%20the%20BJP%2C%20asking%20it%20not%20to%20dig%20up%20historical%20events%20selectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20BJP%20continues%20to%20flip%20through%20history%2C%20people%20will%20also%20remember%20that%20during%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji's%20coronation%2C%20no%20one%20anointed%20him%20by%20hand.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20he%20was%20anointed%20using%20the%20toe%20of%20a%20left%20foot.%20Will%20the%20BJP%20condemn%20this%20today%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20an%20analogy%2C%20Yadav%20referred%20to%20Galileo's%20persecution%20for%20his%20claim%20that%20the%20Earth%20revolves%20around%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGalileo%20was%20punished%20for%20his%20scientific%20assertion%2C%20and%20centuries%20later%2C%20the%20Church%20apologised%20for%20its%20mistake.%20If%20the%20BJP%20respects%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%2C%20will%20they%20apologise%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20anointed%20with%20a%20left%20foot%20toe%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20WAS%20RANA%20SANGA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20Sanga%20or%20Sangram%20Singh%20I%2C%20the%20grandfather%20of%20Maharana%20Pratap%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beloved%20kings%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20who%20ruled%20Mewar%20from%201508%20to%201528.%20In%20a%20culture%20that%20prizes%20valour%2C%20he%20had%20an%20illustrious%20military%20career%2C%20defeating%20the%20Sultans%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Malwa%20and%20Gujarat%20in%2018%20pitched%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20Babar%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Mughal%20dynasty%2C%20he%20fought%20two%20decisive%20battles%20against-%20decisively%20winning%20the%20one%20in%20Bayana%20in%201527.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20Sanga%20had%20decimated%20the%20Mughal%20army%2C%20over-running%20Babar's%20camp%20and%20carrying%20away%20as%20the%20spoils%20of%20war%20everything%20from%20arms%20and%20ammunition%2C%20musical%20instruments%20and%20even%20tents.%20Some%20of%20these%20items%20are%20on%20display%20in%20the%20museums%20of%20Udaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rana%2C%20though%2C%20lost%20the%20battle%20of%20Khandwa%20two%20months%20later%2C%20when%20Babar%20brought%20in%20his%20cannons.%20After%20the%20battle%2C%20he%20had%20died%20of%20his%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDID%20RANA%20SANGA%20INVITE%20BABAR%20TO%20DELHI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20historical%20evidence%20that%20Rana%20Sanga%20invited%20Babar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDocumentary%20sources%20say%20Babar%2C%20who%20was%20eyeing%20India%20after%20losing%20Samarkand%2C%20was%20invited%20by%20Daulat%20khan%20Lodhi%2C%20a%20relative%20then%20Delhi%20Sultan%20Ibrahim%20Lodhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabur%20defeated%20Ibrahim%20Lodi%20in%20the%20First%20Battle%20of%20Panipat%20in%201526%20and%20founded%20the%20Mughal%20Empire%2C%20which%20ruled%20for%20the%20next%20200%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRana%20Sanga%20had%20already%20defeated%20Ibrahim%20Lodhi%20once%2C%20so%20why%20would%20he%20need%20Babur's%20help%2C%20and%20in%20fact%20Rana%20Sanga%20had%20fought%20against%20Babur%20in%20Bayana%2C%26quot%3B%20pointed%20out%20historian%20Chandraprakash%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBAYANA%20TODAY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20identity%20politics%20being%20played%20out%20over%20the%20contribution%20of%20Rana%20Sanga%2C%20Bayana%2C%2030%20km%20from%20Bharatpur%20where%20his%20great%20battle%20with%20Babur%20took%20place%2C%20lies%20neglected%2C%20forgotten%20and%20forlorn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historical%20fortress%20that%20Rana%20Sanga%20beseiged%20and%20over-ran%20is%20falling%20to%20ruins.%20There%20is%20but%20one%20signboard%20pointing%20visitors%20to%20the%20historic%20battlefield%20of%20Bayana%20where%20the%20war%20was%20fought.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742834940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fr00v4dq8_rana-sanga_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamajwadi-party-bjp-bhajan-lal-ramji-lal-suman-gajendra-shekhawat-huge-row-in-rajasthan-over-rana-sanga-explained-8001663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20massive%20row%20over%20history%20is%20brewing%20in%20Rajasthan%20after%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20leader%20made%20a%20remark%20about%20Rana%20Sanga%2C%20the%2016th%20Century%20ruler%20of%20Mewar%2C%20that%20riled%20up%20the%20leaders%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20Rana%20Sanga%20and%20his%20grandson%20Rana%20Pratap%20are%20revered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamajwadi-party-bjp-bhajan-lal-ramji-lal-suman-gajendra-shekhawat-huge-row-in-rajasthan-over-rana-sanga-explained-8001663%22%2C%22cdnA