e...%20None%20of%20them%20will%20choose%20to%20be%20one%20(so%20they%20can%20avoid%20paying%20global%20tax).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%87%BA%F0%9F%87%B8%20The%20US%20sold%201%2C000%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visas%26quot%3B%20at%20**%245%20million%20each**%20in%20just%20one%20day%2C%20said%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Howard%20Latnik.%20This%20brought%20the%20country%20a%20colossal%20**%245%20billion**.%20The%20program%2C%20which%20grants%20investors%20the%20right%20to%20reside%2C%20is%20in%20extremely%20high%20demand.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FD4DfHC8QAT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FD4DfHC8QAT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Teplitsa%20for%20business%20(%40Teplitsa_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTeplitsa_%2Fstatus%2F1903180773647176114%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2021%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they%20going%20to%20have%2C%20is%20to%20have%20the%20right%20to%20be%20in%20America%20(indefinitely%2C%20and%20at%20any%20time%20they%20want)%20by%20paying%20%245%20million.%20They%20will%20be%20vetted%2C%20so%20they%20will%20be%20good%20people%20-%20those%20who%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20law.%20The%20US%20can%20always%20revoke%20it%20if%20they%20are%20evil%20or%20indulge%20in%20illegal%20activity.%20So%2C%20the%20idea%20is%2C%20for%20example%20-%20If%20I%20were%20not%20an%20American%2C%20and%20lived%20in%20any%20other%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20I%20would%20buy%206%20Gold%20Cards%20-%20One%20for%20me%2C%20one%20for%20my%20wife%2C%20and%20one%20for%20my%20four%20children%2C%20because%20God%20forbid%2C%20if%20some%20disaster%20happens%2C%20I%20want%20to%20have%20the%20option%20and%20the%20right%20to%20just%20go%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20fly%20to%20America.%20And%20for%20the%20US%20to%20just%20welcome%20us%20'home'.%20And%20once%20I'm%2