20UK%20Citizen%2C%20Claims%20Petitioner.%20Home%20Ministry%20Says...%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Ministry%20was%20then%20given%20three%20weeks%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20last%20month%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20is%20hearing%20an%20identical%20plea%20-%20filed%20by%20ex-BJP%20MP%20Subramanian%20Swamy%20in%202019%2C%20directed%20the%20union%20government%20to%20seeks%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Swamy%2C%20who%20first%20raised%20this%20allegation%20in%202015%2C%20told%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20DK%20Upadhyaya%20and%20Justice%20TR%20Gedela%20that%20he%20had%20written%20about%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20citizenship%20status%2C%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20earlier%20observed%20dual%20proceedings%20in%20this%20case%20-%20i.e.%2C%20the%20petition%20in%20Allahabad%20and%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20-%20but%20questioned%20the%20centre%20on%20its%20apparent%20inaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Swamy's%20plea%20is%20based%20on%20claims%20that%20a%20former%20British%20company%20-%20formed%20in%202003%20and%20dissolved%20six%20years%20later%20-%20listed%20Mr%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20UK%20national%20in%20some%20of%20its%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20always%20dismissed%20any%20talk%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi%20being%20anything%20other%20than%20Indian.%20His%20sister%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Indian%20and%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20here...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20himself%20called%20the%20allegation%20%26quot%3Ban%20endeavour%20to%20malign%20my%20name%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742825640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjhpiapb_rahul-gandhi_625x300_08_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourt-gives-centre-4-weeks-to-decide-on-rahul-gandhis-citizenship-after-petition-alleges-he-is-a-british-citizen-7999580%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lucknow%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20given%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20been%20given%20four%20weeks%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20citizenship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcourt-gives-centre-4-weeks-to-decide-on-rahul-gandhis-citizenship-after-petition-alleges-he-is-a-british-citizen-7999580%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Get%20Rid%20Of...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Lawyer%20On%20Impeachment%20Amid%20Judge%20Cash%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%20and%20senior%20advocate%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20has%20called%20for%20a%20forensic%20investigation%20into%20the%20cash-at-home%20scam%20and%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20streamline%20the%20system%20of%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20judges%20instead%20of%20the%20current%20rule%20of%20impeachment.%20The%20only%20constitutional%20action%20against%20judges%2C%20impeachment%2C%20is%20so%20complicated%20that%20in%20the%20last%2075%20years%2C%20no%20judge%20has%20been%20impeached%2C%20despite%20three%20or%20four%20attempts%2C%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20incident%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20dent%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20judicial%20dispensation%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20if%20the%20people%20see%20%26quot%3Bthis%20kind%20of%20thing%20and%20if%20the%20judge%20is%20guilty%2C%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20at%20the%20earliest%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20must%20be%20a%20better%20system%20for%20disciplinary%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20said.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20only%20action%20under%20constitution%20is%20impeachment.%C2%A0Impeachment%20is%20so%20laborious%2C%20complex%20and%20difficult%20that%20no%20impeachment%20has%20taken%20place%20in%2075%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-confirms-transfer-of-justice-yashwant-varma-judge-in-cash-at-home-row-to-allahabad-high-court-7998980%5C%22%3Ediscussing%20the%20case%20of%20Justice%20Yashwant%20Varma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20sitting%20judge%20of%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20from%20whose%20house%20a%20stack%20of%20partially%20burnt%20currency%20notes%20were%20recovered%20on%20March%2014%2C%20the%20night%20of%20Holi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recovery%20was%20made%20by%20the%20fire%20department%2C%20which%20was%20called%20in%20to%20douse%20a%20fire%20at%20the%20Delhi%20bungalow%20of%20the%20judge.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20it%2C%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20also%20questioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20to%20order%20an%20internal%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20a%20police%20investigation%2C%20forensic%20investigation.%20large%20number%20of%20VCDs%2C%20CCTV%20footage.%20This%20evidence%20should%20be%20collated%20to%20get%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20advocate%20also%20questioned%20the%20current%20system%20of%20selection%20of%20judges%20through%20a%20collegium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20old%20debate%20on%20the%20manner%20of%20appointment%20of%20judges%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20disciplinary%20proceedings%20against%20judges%20has%20to%20be%20relooked%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20collegium%20is%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20unsatisfactory%20and%20opaque%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20interpreted%20the%20constitution%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20selectively%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20to%20bring%20in%20sunlight%2010%20years%20ago%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20court.%20If%20the%20NJC%20(National%20Judicial%20Commission)%20was%20bad%2C%20we%20can%20have%20some%20via%20media%2C%20some%20sunlight%2C%20some%20outsiders%2C%20who%20have%20a%20committee%20which%20should%20recommend%20judges%20and%20there%20should%20not%20be%20only%20%26quot%3Bjudges%20selecting%20judges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Varma%20was%20moved%20to%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallahabad-high-court-lawyers-to-go-on-strike-over-transfer-of-justice-yashwant-varma-judge-in-cash-at-home-row-8000175%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllahabad%20High%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%20Today%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20it%20has%20recommended%20his%20transfer%20back%20to%20the%20parent%20court%20-%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20apart%20by%20critics.%20The%20top%20court's%20statement%20that%20the%20transfer%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20burnt%20currency%20has%20also%20been%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20understood%20this%20statement%20(of%20the%20Supreme%20Court)%20that%20this%20transfer%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20cash%20scam.%20According%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20cash%20scam%20that%20he%20is%20proposed%20to%20be%20transferred%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rohatgi%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20come%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20issue%20--%20whether%20the%20judge%20is%20delinquent%2C%20is%20he%20guilty%20of%20moral%20turpitude%20or%20he%20is%20not%20and%20his%20reputation%20is%20being%20blackened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Solicitor%20General%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcollegium-system-not-enough-proper-probe-needed-harish-salve-on-judge-cash-case-7977353%5C%22%3EHarish%20Salve%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20any%20transfer%20should%20be%20put%20on%20hold%20till%20the%20matter%20