20Security%20Adviser%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Energy%20Secretary%20Chris%20Wright%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20delegation.%20The%20visit%20comes%20two%20months%20after%20President%20Trump's%20eldest%20son%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr.%2C%20went%20to%20Greenland%20for%20what%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20private%20visit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20delegation%20visit%20will%20be%20from%20Thursday%2C%20March%2027%20to%20Saturday%2C%20March%2029%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20has%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20repeated%20his%20stance%20that%20the%20US%20aims%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20Greenland%26quot%3B%2C%20almost%20suggesting%20that%20there%20are%20no%20other%20options%20left.%20He%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20Washington's%20use%20of%20force%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20Greenland%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20be%20rich%20in%20mineral%20resources%2C%20part%20of%20the%20US%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreenland's%20outgoing%20prime%20minister%2C%20Mute%20Egede%2C%20has%20called%20the%20high-profile%20US%20visit%20%26quot%3Ba%20provocation%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20that%20they%20are%20not%20welcome%20in%20the%20country.%20Stopping%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20military%20base%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20due%20to%20treaty%20obligations%2C%20but%20the%20interim%20government%20will%20not%20be%20meeting%20the%20US%20delegation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20recently%2C%20we%20could%20trust%20the%20Americans%2C%20who%20were%20our%20allies%20and%20friends%2C%20and%20with%20whom%20we%20enjoyed%20working%20very%20closely%2C%20but%20that%20time%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Greenland's%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Greenlandic%20government%2C%20Naalakkersuisut%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20a%20caretaker%20phase%20following%20a%20March%2011%20parliamentary%