%20and%20advances%20economic%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Brian%20Hughes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agency%20Reuters%2C%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20visit%2C%20Washington%20has%20already%20sent%20two%20US%20Hercules%20military%20transport%20planes%2C%20carrying%20security%20personnel%20and%20bulletproof%20vehicles.%20Denmark%20has%20also%20sent%20dozens%20of%20police%20personnel%20to%20Greenland's%20capital%20Nuuk%20to%20boost%20the%20delegation's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20and%20Energy%20Secretary%20plan%20to%20visit%20US'%20space%20base%20in%20Pituffik%2C%20which%20is%20located%20along%20the%20shortest%20route%20from%20Europe%20to%20North%20America%2C%20and%20is%20vital%20for%20ballistic%20missile%20warning%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Mette%20Frederiksen%20said%20that%20the%20top%20US%20delegation%20announcing%20a%20visit%20is%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20we%20take%20very%20seriously%26quot%3B.%20She%20added%20that%20on%20matters%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fundamental%20rules%20of%20sovereignty%26quot%3B%2C%20Denmark%20expects%20the%20United%20States%20to%20respect%20Copenhagen%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Greenland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20Reuters)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742820180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fcq8i0su8_usha-vance-us-second-lady-usha-vance-afp_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgreenland-furious-will-boycott-us-second-ladys-visit-amid-buyout-threats-7999773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Displeased%20would%20be%20an%20understatement%20to%20describe%20the%20way%20leaders%20in%20Greenland%20are%20feeling%20about%20the%20planned%20visit%20of%20the%20Second%20Lady%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Usha%20Vance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0