%20of%20tweets%20criticising%20the%20judiciary%20following%20the%20court's%20decision%20to%20grant%20bail%20to%20journalist%20Arnab%20Goswami.%20He%20had%20mocked%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20had%20taken%20to%20Twitter%20soon%20after%20Mr%20Goswami%20was%20released%20on%20interim%20bail%20in%20an%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20case.%20In%20his%20first%20post%20on%20X%20(then%20known%20as%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%26quot%3BSupreme%20Joke%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20This%20was%20followed%20up%20by%20a%20morphed%20photo%20that%20showed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20saffron%20with%20a%20BJP%20flag%20flying%20over%20it.%20He%20made%20scathing%20remarks%20attacking%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20by%20comparing%20him%20to%20a%20flight%20attendant%20serving%20champagne%20to%20first-class%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202020%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Kamra%20over%20his%20tweets.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20explain%20why%20action%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20against%20him%20for%20contempt%20of%20court.%20Mr%20Kamra%20publicly%20said%20he%20won't%20apologise%20for%20his%20tweets.%20In%20his%20official%20response%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20he%20defended%20his%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20and%20refused%20to%20retract%20his%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Brahmin-Baniya'%20Remark%20On%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202020%2C%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20Mr%20Kamra%20for%20his%20remark%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BBrahmin-Baniya%26quot%3B%20affair%20in%20his%20show%20'Be%20Like'.%20The%20petition%20was%20filed%20as%20an%20intervention%20application%20in%20an%20already%20pending%20contempt%20of%20court%20case%20against%20Mr%20Kamra.%20Attorney-General%20KK%20Venugopal%20had%20approved%20a%20contempt%20proceeding%20against%20Mr%20Kamra%20for%20allegedly%20disparaging%20the%20judiciary%20and%20judges%20through%20his%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAirport%20Incident%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20confronted%20Mr%20Goswami%20during%20a%20flight%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20ban%20from%20major%20airlines%20like%20IndiGo%2C%20Air%20India%2C%20GoAir%20and%20SpiceJet%20for%20six%20months.%20While%20not%20a%20formal%20legal%20case%2C%20this%20incident%20sparked%20widespread%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20harassed%20and%20heckled%20Mr%20Goswami%20on%20a%20January%202020%20trip%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Lucknow.%20Mr%20Kamra%20then%20turned%20to%20Twitter%20to%20share%20a%20clip%20of%20himself%20heckling%20the%20journalist.%20He%20also%20tweeted%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonologue%26quot%3B%20with%20Mr%20Goswami%20on%20his%20journalism.%20He%20called%20Mr%20Goswami%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoward%26quot%3B%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20He%20closed%20the%20tweet%20with%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bf***%20Arnab%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20Mr%20Goswami%20failed%20to%20respond%20and%20labelled%20him%20mentally%20insane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttacks%20On%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20Over%20Covid%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Mr%20Kamra%20made%20serious%20allegations%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20handling%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20crisis%20in%20an%20opinion%20video.%20He%20accused%20PM%20Modi%20of%20putting%20political%20vanity%20before%20common%20sense%20and%20opening%20the%20door%20to%20a%20devastating%20resurgence%20of%20coronavirus%20infections.%20Mr%20Kamra%20said%20had%20PM%20Modi%20and%20other%20political%20leaders%20responded%20quickly%20and%20effectively%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20lives%20and%20heartache%20would%20have%20been%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChild's%20'Morphed'%20Video%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202020%2C%20Mr%20Kamra%20landed%20in%20a%20controversy%20for%20sharing%20an%20edited%20video%20of%20a%20seven-year-old%20boy%20singing%20for%20PM%20Modi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Germany.%20The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%20sought%20action%20against%20the%20comedian%20for%20posting%20a%20%26quot%3Bdoctored%26quot%3B%20video%20of%20a%20boy%20singing%20a%20patriotic%20song%20in%20front%20of%20PM%20Modi.%20The%20NCPCR%20also%20sought%20immediate%20removal%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%2C%20Mr%20Kamra%20said%20the%20video%20was%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20posted%20by%20a%20news%20organisation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20joke%20is%20not%20on%20your%20son%2C%20while%20you%20enjoy%20your%20son%20sing%20for%20his%20motherland%20to%20the%20most%20popular%20son%2C%20there%20are%20songs%20that%20he%20should%20listen%20to%20from%20people%20of%20his%20country%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamra%20posted.%20In%20another%20post%2C%20he%20said%20the%20NCPCR%20sought%20action%20against%20him%20for%20posting%20a%20%26quot%3Bmeme%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E'%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20lawyer%20Chandni%20Preeti%20Vijaykumar%20Shah%20wrote%20to%20Attorney%20General%20KK%20Venugopal%20seeking%20to%20initiate%20criminal%20proceedings%20against%20the%20comedian%20under%20the%20State%20Emblem%20of%20India%20(Prohibition%20of%20Improper%20Use)%20Act%2C%202005.%20Mr%20Kamra%20insulted%20India's%20national%20emblem%20by%20using%20it%20in%20a%20morphed%20certificate%20that%20shamed%20the%20agony%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandit%20genocide%20and%20blatantly%20mocked%20the%20film%20'The%20Kashmir%20Files'%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20lawyers%20-%20Ashutosh%20Dubey%20and%20Vineet%20Jindal%20-%20in%20the%20same%20month%20also%20wrote%20to%20Mr%20Venugopal%20requesting%20permission%20to%20start%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20stand-up%20comedian%20for%20vilifying%20and%20defaming%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20in%20his%20recent%20comedy%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20Notice%20From%20VHP%20Over%20Alleged%20Insult%20To%20Hindu%20Deities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra's%20show%20in%20Gurugram%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20club%20that%20was%20to%20host%20it%20after%20some%20right-wing%20organisations%20threatened%20protests%20over%20his%20jokes%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Binsulting%20Hindu%20gods%26quot%3B.%20The%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20sent%20Mr%20Kamra%20a%20legal%20notice%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20insulting%20Hindu%20gods%20in%20his%20comedy%20shows.%20They%20demanded%20an%20apology%20and%20warned%20of%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20Mr%20Kamra%20wrote%20to%20the%20VHP%20asking%20it%20to%20denounce%20Mahatma%20Gandhi's%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20outfit%20is%20pro-Hindu%20and%20anti-terrorism.%20He%20also%20asked%20them%20to%20show%20proof%20that%20he%20disrespected%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlleged%20Harassment%20Of%20Women%20Comedians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20which%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20in%202020%2C%20a%20woman%20named%20Anubha%20Sinha%20alleged%20comedians%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20%23MeToo%20accused%20Utsav%20Chakraborty%20made%20fake%20X%20IDs%20to%20harass%20fellow%20women%20comedians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sinha%20said%20she%20overheard%20Mr%20Kamra%20say%20that%20Mr%20Chakraborty%20and%20himself%20would%20make%20fake%20accounts%20on%20X%20to%20harass%20women%20standup%20comedians.%20Ms%20Sinha%20said%20she%20did%20not%20write%20about%20it%20earlier%2C%20but%20after%20Mr%20Kamra%20heckled%20the%20Republic%20TV%20Editor-in-Chief%20on%20an%20Indigo%20flight%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20write%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKunal%20Kamra's%20Challenge%20To%20IT%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20issued%20the%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Media%20Ethics%20Code)%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202023%20(IT%20Rules%202023).%20These%20rules%20direct%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20(such%20as%20Facebook%2C%20Twitter%2C%20etc)%20to%20remove%20any%20news%20related%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20of%20the%20central%20government%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bfake%2C%20false%2C%20or%20misleading%26quot%3B%20by%20a%20fact-checking%20unit%20established%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20challenged%20the%20rules%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20He%20said%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20fact-check%20unit%20is%20in%20conflict%20with%20Section%2079%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000%20(IT%20Act)%20which%20is%20a%20safe%20harbour%20provision%20for%20social%20media%20intermediaries.%20It%20protects%20them%20from%20liability%20for%20user-generated%20content.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20decide%20if%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20notification%20of%20a%20government%20fact%20check%20unit%20under%20the%20IT%20Rules%2C%202023%20can%20be%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20Of%20Election%20Commission%20And%20EVMs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kamra%20mocked%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20use%20of%20EVMs%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20in%20various%20posts%20and%20videos.%20This%20led%20to%20complaints%20from%20political%20groups%2C%20although%20no%20legal%20action%20was%20officially%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742819520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fpsfq6gbo_kunal-kamra_625x300_24_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F10-times-when-comedian-kunal-kamra-ran-into-controversies-7999668%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20Mumbai%20event%20was%20disrupted%20by%20