%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g0718g3jwo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4g0718g3jwo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meerut%20Murder%20Accused%20Long-Time%20Drug%20Abusers%2C%20Were%20Intoxicated%20Before%20Crime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%20arrested%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20former%20Merchant%20Navy%20officer%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Meerut%20have%20been%20long-time%20abusers%20of%20dry%20and%20injectable%20drugs%20and%20had%20consumed%20psychotropic%20substances%20before%20committing%20the%20crime%20on%20March%204%2C%20probe%20officials%20said%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20Rastogi%20and%20her%20lover%20Sahil%20Shukla%2C%20who%20brutally%20killed%20her%20husband%20Saurabh%20Rajput%2C%20have%20been%20addicted%20to%20drugs%20since%202019.%20The%20duo%20consumed%20drugs%20before%20carrying%20out%20the%20murder%20and%20later%20travelled%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Kasol%20in%20search%20of%20more%20substances%2C%20the%20officials%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20emerged%20as%20officials%20began%20interrogating%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20in%20the%20murder%20case.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20an%20earlier%20occasion%20too%2C%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%20had%20visited%20Manali%20and%20Kasol%20for%20drugs.%20The%20accused%20will%20be%20counselled%20for%20about%2015%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20jail%20superintendent%20Viresh%20Raj%20Sharma%20on%20Sunday%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20the%20two%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdrugs-craving-no-conversations-meerut-murder-accuseds-days-in-prison-7990037%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiencing%20withdrawal%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20are%20being%20provided%20treatment.%20The%20duo%20wanted%20to%20be%20lodged%20in%20the%20same%20barrack%20but%20were%20told%20that%20as%20per%20rules%2C%20it%20was%20not%20possible%2C%20the%20officials%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20cab%20driver%20who%20was%20hired%20to%20take%20the%20accused%20from%20Meerut%20to%20Shimla%2C%20Manali%20and%20Kasol%20said%20Sahil%20used%20to%20regularly%20purchase%20alcohol%20and%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-murder-case-update-latest-news-accused-trip-himachal-pradesh-vacation-former-merchant-navy-officer-7986073%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrink%20at%20least%20two%20bottles%20everyday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Muskaan%20had%20also%20consumed%20alcohol%20while%20they%20were%20returning%20to%20Meerut%20after%20the%20trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20Muskaan%20and%20Sahil%2C%20her%20lover%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-cement-murder-up-woman-lover-kill-husband-body-chopped-up-sealed-with-cement-in-drum-7957211%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estabbed%20her%20husband%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dismembered%20his%20body%2C%20before%20sealing%20the%20parts%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-saurabh-rajput-murder-muskaan-rastogi-meerut-killers-muskaan-sahil-made-a-mistake-that-cost-them-heavily-7996949%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrum%20with%20cement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Police%20earlier%20said%20that%20Saurabh%20was%20allegedly%20drugged%20before%20his%20murder.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20probe%20officials%20said%20Muskaan%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-murder-case-news-today-accused-wife-husband-lover-sleeping-pills-usha-medical-store-7993040%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etampered%20with%20her%20husband's%20prescription%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20purchase%20sleeping%20pills%20to%20drug%20him%20before%20killing%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20committing%20the%20crime%20on%20March%204%2C%20Muskaan%20and%